      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in superlative condition, having been curated with fastidious attention to detail and maintained to an exacting standard. Every surface reflects a commitment to preservation, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. For the discerning enthusiast who accepts only the absolute finest, this represents a rare acquisition opportunity of investment-grade quality.",
